    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted given the standardized single-configuration nature of the ASTM F1717 protocol and the conservative acceptance bounds applied. All QoI comparisons pass the pre-established normalized error and percentage difference criteria. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the Medium assurance level required for this Class II device submission.",
